Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&Hb047de&}{\fad(500,200)}cosplay咖啡厅\N\N「白骑士」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.16,0:00:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然就今天一天 做花怜学姐的临时救兵是没问题啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.87,0:00:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女仆咖啡厅的女侍应生啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 不过 凡事重在经历
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.71,0:00:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定总有一天会对潜入调查起作用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.38,0:00:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 虽然前段时间的校服也挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.74,0:00:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件也挺美～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.84,0:00:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换好衣服了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.59,0:00:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.69,0:00:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.60,0:00:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是代替美波野小姐的侍应生？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.55,0:00:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫白鸟美由 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.90,0:00:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫皇蓝华 请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.44,0:00:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是现役女子高中生 皮肤果然光滑水嫩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.38,0:00:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我也还挺...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:00:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我还有相应的大人魅力补救
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.48,0:01:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不如理沙子老师那样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.46,0:01:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起绘理我可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.12,0:01:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐跟美波野小姐是什么关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.06,0:01:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 哦 呃...学生时代时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.30,0:01:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 现在也是学生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.02,0:01:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是她社团的学妹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学妹？你？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.39,0:01:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.57,0:01:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花怜学姐是那种体质嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.55,0:01:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从以前开始 我就经常被别人误以为比她大 ha ha ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.03,0:01:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花怜学姐 「因为是克隆体 是永远的17岁」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.52,0:01:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个设定会不会太扯淡了一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.27,0:01:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般来说 没人会接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.88,0:01:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.45,0:01:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的客人有着各种兴趣喜好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.08,0:01:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.85,0:01:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来 你在接客方面应该没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 还好吧 能搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.49,0:01:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看美波野小姐那样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是这家店的No.2
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.12,0:01:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你得相当努力才行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.94,0:01:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...多嘴问一句 No.1是？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:01:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.91,0:01:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.23,0:02:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.1还是2什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.45,0:02:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家是什么店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.08,0:02:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 离开店还有点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.92,0:02:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来练习练习
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐 你这算什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.52,0:02:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.50,0:02:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家店可不是女仆咖啡厅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃？！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.73,0:02:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是根正苗红且格调高雅的咖啡厅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.09,0:02:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 穿成这样还好意思说格调高雅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.26,0:02:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花怜学姐可是戴猫耳上班的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.78,0:02:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...咳咳 欢迎光临喵～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.37,0:02:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫你模仿美波野小姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你来弄一点也都不可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.88,0:02:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按普通的重新来一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.98,0:02:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临 要点些什...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的 你到这里坐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.87,0:02:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来做一遍当示范
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.18,0:02:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.20,0:02:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 你一开始就应该这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢淫光临～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 小姐你哪位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不不不不不不 没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.09,0:03:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请继续
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.27,0:03:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙太猛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 她脑子里面是不是还有另一重人格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要点些什么呢？决定好了吗～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.30,0:03:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 呃...我要冰咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.08,0:03:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一杯冰咖啡是吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.85,0:03:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白鸟～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.86,0:03:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这果然是女仆咖啡店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 你来试一试
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢～迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.09,0:03:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 要更可爱一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.45,0:03:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎～光临
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要更优雅一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.80,0:03:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢 欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.28,0:03:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有包含心意在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.47,0:03:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭迎肛临！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 要被干了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.26,0:03:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认真来做 还是很行的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.39,0:03:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样接客 客人一定会很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就按照刚才那样来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.49,0:03:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天全天都努力工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:03:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 要开店了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.03,0:04:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错！是「请多肛照」才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.88,0:04:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多肛照了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.51,0:04:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～打烊以后 你留下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.78,0:04:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.46,0:04:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 稍 稍等...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打烊后留下来 这不就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她该不会是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非...糟糕 闪人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退！
